For self-hosting convenience, this distribution bundles components of the Supabase
self-hosted stack under `selfhost/` — Postgres, GoTrue (Auth), PostgREST, Realtime,
Storage, Kong, edge-runtime, and Studio. Those components are the property of their
respective authors and are licensed under their own terms (Supabase's own components are
largely Apache-2.0; bundled databases/services carry PostgreSQL, MIT, and similar licenses).

`selfhost/docker-compose.yml`, `selfhost/volumes/`, and the Caddy TLS overlay
(`selfhost/docker-compose.caddy.yml`, `selfhost/volumes/proxy/caddy/`) are adapted from the
upstream `supabase/supabase` repository (Apache-2.0).

No endorsement by Supabase, Inc. is implied.
